description: Veraci Pizza is Seattle's original, award-winning traveling wood-fired pizza company.We specialize in creating authentic Italian pizza at Farmer's Markets, festivals & private partiesWe don't deliver pizza -we bring the whole wood-fired ovenand pizza making operation to your event!  With our custom-made wood-fired pizza oven we come to your venue,fire-up our ovenand start making pizzas!Service time lasts for 2 hours while we mix and matchyour choice of toppings to create fresh, hot authentic pizzas.
name: Veraci Pizza
